---
title: Turkey Biryani with Peas and Sweet Pepper
description: Biryani or 'spiced rice' is an Indian mixed rice dish. A combination of onions, garlic, ginger and dal spices makes this dish absolutely burst with flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/turkey-biryani-6af60ca0.jpg
